WMG (Windows) setup instructions
--------------------------------

Download and install ActivePerl:
http://downloads.activestate.com/ActivePerl/Windows/5.8/ActivePerl-5.8.7.815-MSWin32-x86-211909.msi

Run Start menu > Programs > ActivePerl 5.8.1 build 815 > Perl package manager
Type at the ppm> prompt:
install XML-RSS
(wait for it to finish, then)
exit

Download and install ImageMagick:
http://www.imagemagick.org/download/binaries/ImageMagick-6.2.6-3-Q16-windows-dll.exe
